title: Rates on Customer Loans for New York, NY
notes:
Series Is Presented Here As Two Variables--(1)--Original Data, 1919-1939 (2)--Original Data, 1948-1959. Data Are For Weighted Averages Of Prevailing Rates. Source: Federal Reserve Board, Annual Report For 1931, P. 82 And Successive Reports; Federal Reserve Bulletin, October 1939, P. 908.
